uhur\/","url_meta":{"origin":15014,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Suhur: Blessings in pre-fasting morning meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTake the pre-fasting meal, for surely there are blessings in the pre-fasting meal.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1923, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1095 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14885,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/come-to-blessed-suhur\/","url_meta":{"origin":15014,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Come to the blessed pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-'Irbad ibn Sariyah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, invited me to the pre-fasting meal\u00a0during Ramadan and he said, \u201cOnward to the blessed meal!\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2344 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u0650\u0631\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0636\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u062f\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650\u064a \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0